criteria.textblock:
        -  Caucasian;

          -  female;

          -  age 30-45 years;

          -  Body Mass Index (BMI)>30 m/kg2;

          -  non-smoker;

          -  not pregnant or lactating;

          -  Restraint Scale (Herman and Polivy, 1988) score >15, indicating a history of chronic
             dieting;

          -  no recent myocardial infarction;

          -  no active neoplasms, Type 1 diabetes or insulin-dependent Type 2 diabetes, nor history
             of cerebrovascular or renal disease.
